{"tid":2013130,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"可唔可以司法覆核上屆內會主席無權召開今屆會議？","createTime":"2020-05-12T06:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T08:57:41.000Z","uid":130981,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b4d28ab3acffcee5a620ec19804b25f4c14940","tid":2013130,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:17:09.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;司法覆核是用來判定公共機構在行動上的合法性&rdquo;<br />\n而家擺到明違反議事規則<br />\n司法覆核就一招試到所謂司法獨立到底有幾獨立<br />\n定係三權合作為共產黨服務<br />\n<br />\n你喺規矩內玩 搵到漏洞<br />\n對家直接反枱<br />\n係時候叫裁判<br />\n如果裁判最基本嘅公平公正都做唔到 咁佢地都冇值得尊重嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b92ae82964fbb988ddfba10c48dbe2ce23ce4e","tid":2013130,"uid":31151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"佢係有權召開會議 但新一屆會議第一議程必定係選主席"},{"pid":"a208e1f33b67b5a2656573dee9fc5774dbd92266","tid":2013130,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"都唔影響國歌法，因為政府同內務委員會主席磋商就可以恢復二讀，唔需要再開內會。"},{"pid":"6c61b14885844141b0e58ea363bea4e1425692a3","tid":2013130,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a208e1f33b67b5a2656573dee9fc5774dbd92266","tid":2013130,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"都唔影響國歌法，因為政府同內務委員會主席磋商就可以恢復二讀，唔需要再開內會。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"咁上屆主席有權？"},{"pid":"773a55e62f357baae89c0f6a2f7fac28d918d111","tid":2013130,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"申請咗禁制令先"},{"pid":"17260e821f9afd74c3c88059039b77de4cdde3f6","tid":2013130,"uid":2837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecb49749738c5bcc5c8d6bf343dc144bf62f8962","tid":2013130,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b4d28ab3acffcee5a620ec19804b25f4c14940","tid":2013130,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit